    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/30eacbc05256b2ae99d76aa1175013f7.poster.avif?t=1633091963\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/30eacbc05256b2ae99d76aa1175013f7.webm?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/30eacbc05256b2ae99d76aa1175013f7.mp4?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>米斯特尔(Mistral)是一款快节奏的动作漫游游戏，专注于可重玩性。探索米斯特尔的土地，寻找遗物来升级你的角色能力，并战胜你的敌人。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>独特的战斗风格，掌握每一种武器的优势!<br></li><li>有层次的角色升级系统，广大的物品选择。为你的探险制定的策略!<br></li><li>死亡并不是游戏的结束，解锁威力，获得永久的强大力量以应付下一轮。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >具有挑战性的游戏模式和动态的战斗机制.</h2> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/890ceb7354dfe151ca4013847769e28c.poster.avif?t=1633091963\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/890ceb7354dfe151ca4013847769e28c.webm?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/890ceb7354dfe151ca4013847769e28c.mp4?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在探索世界时，环境设置都会发生变化.</h2> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/6f221c07df6e3362310e51124ebc2f24.poster.avif?t=1633091963\" width=600 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/6f221c07df6e3362310e51124ebc2f24.webm?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/6f221c07df6e3362310e51124ebc2f24.mp4?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与你的朋友在合作模式下一起探险（最多8人）。或交新朋友.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/3d05dce1a5b08b01e9ba97a52b3cf282.poster.avif?t=1633091963\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/3d05dce1a5b08b01e9ba97a52b3cf282.webm?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756710/extras/3d05dce1a5b08b01e9ba97a52b3cf282.mp4?t=1633091963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
